Paper: hep-th/9405066

Date: 1994-05-10

Title: The role of the superstring dilaton in cosmology and particle physics

Authors: R. Brustein

Comments: Latex, 12 pages, preprint CERN-TH.7255/94

Superstring theory predicts the existence of a scalar field, the dilaton. Ireview some basic features of the dilaton interactions and explain theirpossible consequences in cosmology and particle physics.